723502f-a.title: Manhattan: Thayer Street - Sherman Avenue
723502f-a.text:
Thayer Street, west side, south from but not including Sherman
Ave., showing a row of apartment houses at the N.W. corner of Nagle Ave.
Backed up to same and appearing as a unit are similar houses at the N.E.
corner of Nagle Ave. and Arden Street; the latter paralleling Thayer
Street on the west.
October 26, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
